---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';

const lastUpdated = 'February 13, 2026';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy & Legal" description="Privacy policy, terms of use, and digital asset disclaimers for Inspired Mile.">

  <section class="section-padding">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-display font-bold mb-4">
        Privacy Policy & <span class="text-gradient">Legal</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-obsidian-500 text-sm mb-12">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

      <!-- Company Identity -->
      <div class="card-glass p-6 mb-8">
        <h2 class="font-display text-lg font-bold text-obsidian-100 mb-2">Company Information</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-obsidian-400 leading-relaxed">
          Inspired Mile is a product of <strong class="text-obsidian-200">Voyage Tracable, LLC</strong>,
          a limited liability company registered in the state of Florida.
          All references to "Inspired Mile," "we," "us," or "our" on this website refer to
          Voyage Tracable, LLC operating under the DBA "Inspired Mile."
        </p>
        <p class="text-xs text-obsidian-500 mt-2">Sarasota, FL &middot; United States</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Privacy Policy -->
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-gold-300 mb-4">1. Privacy Policy</h2>

          <h3 class="font-display text-sm font-semibold text-obsidian-200 mb-2 mt-6">1.1 Data Collection</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-obsidian-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">
            Inspired Mile is designed with privacy as a core principle. Our AI features (including the
            Master Thespian battle system, text-to-speech, and speech-to-text) run <strong class="text-obsidian-200">entirely
            in your browser</strong> using WebGPU and WebAssembly. No conversation data, voice recordings,
            or AI interactions are transmitted to our servers or any third party.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-obsidian-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">
            We collect minimal data necessary to operate the platform:
          </p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-obsidian-400 space-y-1 ml-4 list-disc">
            <li>Basic analytics (page views, anonymized usage patterns)</li>
            <li>Wallet addresses if you voluntarily connect a wallet for NFT features</li>
            <li>Email address if you voluntarily subscribe to updates</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="font-display text-sm font-semibold text-obsidian-200 mb-2 mt-6">1.2 Local Storage</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-obsidian-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">
            Your card inventory, game progress, and preferences are stored locally in your browser
            using localStorage and IndexedDB. This data remains on your device and is not transmitted
            to our servers. Clearing your browser data will delete this information.
          </p>

          <h3 class="font-display text-sm font-semibold text-obsidian-200 mb-2 mt-6">1.3 AI Model Data</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-obsidian-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">
            AI models are downloaded once from public model repositories and cached in your browser.
            All inference (text generation, speech synthesis, speech recognition) happens locally on
            your device. <strong class="text-obsidian-200">No prompts, conversations, or audio data are sent to any server.</strong>
          </p>

          <h3 class="font-display text-sm font-semibold text-obsidian-200 mb-2 mt-6">1.4 Third-Party Services</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-obsidian-400 leading-relaxed">
            If you connect a third-party wallet (e.g., Phantom, Solflare) or interact with
            blockchain networks, those interactions are governed by the respective third-party
            privacy policies. We do not control and are not responsible for the data practices
            of third-party wallet providers or blockchain networks.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Digital Assets / NFT Disclaimers -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-gold-300 mb-4">2. Digital Asset Disclaimers</h2>

          <div class="card-glass p-5 bg-crimson-500/5 border-crimson-500/20 mb-6">
            <p class="text-sm text-crimson-300 font-semibold mb-2">Important Notice Regarding Digital Assets</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-obsidian-400 leading-relaxed">
              Please read this section carefully before using any digital asset or NFT features
              on the Inspired Mile platform.
            </p>
          </div>

          <h3 class="font-display text-sm font-semibold text-obsidian-200 mb-2 mt-6">2.1 Not a Cryptocurrency Creator</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-obsidian-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">
            Voyage Tracable, LLC (DBA Inspired Mile) <strong class="text-obsidian-200">does not create, issue, or manage
            any cryptocurrency, token, or coin</strong>. We do not operate a token sale, initial coin offering
            (ICO), or any form of securities offering. The digital cards within our platform are
            digital collectibles (non-fungible tokens / NFTs) intended for entertainment and gameplay
            purposes only.
          </p>

          <h3 class="font-display text-sm font-semibold text-obsidian-200 mb-2 mt-6">2.2 Not a Custodian</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-obsidian-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">
            Voyage Tracable, LLC <strong class="text-obsidian-200">is not a custodian, trustee, or fiduciary</strong> of any
            user's digital assets, cryptocurrency, or NFTs. When you mint a card as an NFT,
            ownership and control of that asset transfers to your personal wallet. We do not
            hold, store, manage, or have access to your wallet, private keys, or on-chain assets.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-obsidian-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">
            You are solely responsible for:
          </p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-obsidian-400 space-y-1 ml-4 list-disc">
            <li>Safeguarding your wallet credentials and private keys</li>
            <li>Any transactions you initiate from your wallet</li>
            <li>Understanding the risks associated with blockchain transactions</li>
            <li>Complying with applicable laws and tax obligations in your jurisdiction</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="font-display text-sm font-semibold text-obsidian-200 mb-2 mt-6">2.3 Nature of Digital Collectibles</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-obsidian-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">
            Digital cards within Inspired Mile are collectible game items. When optionally minted
            as NFTs, they represent proof of ownership of a unique digital item on a public blockchain.
            They are <strong class="text-obsidian-200">not</strong>:
          </p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-obsidian-400 space-y-1 ml-4 list-disc">
            <li>Securities, investment contracts, or financial instruments</li>
            <li>Currency, stablecoins, or stores of value</li>
            <li>Guaranteed to hold, increase, or maintain any monetary value</li>
            <li>Redeemable for cash, fiat currency, or cryptocurrency from Voyage Tracable, LLC</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="font-display text-sm font-semibold text-obsidian-200 mb-2 mt-6">2.4 No Investment Advice</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-obsidian-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">
            Nothing on this platform constitutes financial, investment, legal, or tax advice.
            Digital assets, including NFTs, are speculative and carry significant risk. Values
            can fluctuate dramatically and you may lose some or all of your purchase value.
            Consult a qualified professional before making any financial decisions related to
            digital assets.
          </p>

          <h3 class="font-display text-sm font-semibold text-obsidian-200 mb-2 mt-6">2.5 Blockchain Risks</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-obsidian-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">
            Blockchain transactions are irreversible. Once a transaction is confirmed on-chain,
            it cannot be undone, reversed, or refunded by Voyage Tracable, LLC. You acknowledge
            and accept the inherent risks of blockchain technology, including but not limited to:
          </p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-obsidian-400 space-y-1 ml-4 list-disc">
            <li>Smart contract vulnerabilities or bugs</li>
            <li>Network congestion, delays, or failures</li>
            <li>Changes to blockchain protocols or consensus mechanisms</li>
            <li>Regulatory changes that may affect the legality or usability of digital assets</li>
            <li>Loss of access due to lost private keys or wallet credentials</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="font-display text-sm font-semibold text-obsidian-200 mb-2 mt-6">2.6 Marketplace</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-obsidian-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">
            Any marketplace features provided by Inspired Mile facilitate peer-to-peer transactions
            between users. Voyage Tracable, LLC acts as a <strong class="text-obsidian-200">platform provider only</strong> and is not
            a party to transactions between buyers and sellers. We do not guarantee the completion,
            accuracy, or legality of any transaction conducted through the platform. Marketplace
            fees, if any, will be clearly disclosed before each transaction.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Intellectual Property -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-gold-300 mb-4">3. Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-obsidian-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">
            The Inspired Mile brand, logo, card designs, AI character personas (including the
            "Master Thespian"), and original artwork are the property of Voyage Tracable, LLC.
            Shakespeare's original works are in the public domain.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-obsidian-400 leading-relaxed">
            Purchasing or earning a digital card grants you a personal, non-exclusive, non-transferable
            license to display and use the card within the Inspired Mile platform for personal,
            non-commercial purposes. Minting a card as an NFT grants ownership of the token but
            does not transfer copyright or commercial rights to the underlying artwork or content.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Terms of Use -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-gold-300 mb-4">4. Terms of Use</h2>

          <h3 class="font-display text-sm font-semibold text-obsidian-200 mb-2 mt-6">4.1 Eligibility</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-obsidian-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">
            You must be at least 13 years of age to use the Inspired Mile platform. Users under 18
            should obtain parental or guardian consent before interacting with any digital asset or
            NFT features. NFT minting, purchasing, and trading features require users to be at
            least 18 years of age or the age of majority in their jurisdiction.
          </p>

          <h3 class="font-display text-sm font-semibold text-obsidian-200 mb-2 mt-6">4.2 Acceptable Use</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-obsidian-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">
            You agree not to use the platform to:
          </p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-obsidian-400 space-y-1 ml-4 list-disc">
            <li>Manipulate or exploit game mechanics, marketplace pricing, or ranking systems</li>
            <li>Engage in money laundering, fraud, or other illegal activities</li>
            <li>Harass, abuse, or harm other users</li>
            <li>Infringe upon intellectual property rights</li>
            <li>Reverse engineer, decompile, or tamper with the platform's systems</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="font-display text-sm font-semibold text-obsidian-200 mb-2 mt-6">4.3 Limitation of Liability</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-obsidian-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">
            The Inspired Mile platform is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind. To the
            maximum extent permitted by law, Voyage Tracable, LLC shall not be liable for any
            indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages arising from your
            use of the platform, including but not limited to loss of digital assets, loss of
            data, or inability to access your cards or NFTs.
          </p>

          <h3 class="font-display text-sm font-semibold text-obsidian-200 mb-2 mt-6">4.4 Governing Law</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-obsidian-400 leading-relaxed">
            These terms are governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the State
            of Florida, without regard to its conflict of law provisions.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Contact -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-gold-300 mb-4">5. Contact</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-obsidian-400 leading-relaxed">
            For questions about this privacy policy, terms of use, or digital asset practices,
            please contact Voyage Tracable, LLC at the information provided on our
            <a href="/about" class="text-gold-400 hover:text-gold-300 transition-colors">About</a> page.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
